{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in our uniforms, and when they got torn or something, the Germans have captured enough stores of French Army to give a-- give us another pair of pants or another jacket, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have to say that they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what happened later on when I was picked out to go the Jewish camp, whether somebody pointed me out or not.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did not feel antisemitism coming from the people I was with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would-- just to-- you know, in Traunstein, what we were doing, my-- our basic work after this agriculture thing-- our basic work that we were doing there was maintaining the-- the railroad tracks, which is hard work, you know, laying tracks and so on.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was an old railroad man who was directing that work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wasn't guarding us, but he was telling us what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this man, every evening, would get on his bicycle and go to all the pubs in the area and pick up all the cigarette stubs, go home, empty them, and in the morning, he would give every one of us a pinch of tobacco.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that point, we didn't have anything to smoke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were all smokers, and it was-- I think that we have to talk about the things that we have-- I-- that I  have encountered which were kindness-- which were kindness.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not everything was-- was terrible, and not everything was brutality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was also kindness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know whether he-- yes, probably if some crazy Hitler follower would know about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to understand that we were in Bavaria, a strongly Catholic country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not for Hitler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hitler persecuted Catholics also.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
